@startuml MyAIStorybook_SSD_Export_PDF
title MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Export Story to PDF Scenario

actor "User" as User
participant ":System" as System

note over User, System
    Export Story to PDF Scenario (Main Success)
    System is treated as BLACK BOX
end note

User -> System : selectStory(story_id)
System --> User : story_details

User -> System : requestPDFExport()
System --> User : export_started

System --> User : pdf_ready(file_path, download_url)

User -> System : downloadPDF()
System --> User : pdf_file

note right of System
    System generates PDF internally
    with story text and images
    Returns downloadable file
end note

@enduml
